OL,3,C'An amazing way to start the day':
OL,4,CSwimmers make a splash in Alderney
OL,6,FSea swims are part of island life but
OL,7,Ffor one group in Alderney, it's become
OL,8,Fa regular ritual.
OL,10,FThe 'Alderney Swim and Soup' group
OL,11,Fhave been meeting every day for nearly
OL,12,Ffour years, enjoying an early morning
OL,13,Fdip and then a cup of homemade soup to
OL,14,Fwarm up afterwards.
OL,16,FSea swimming is said to have huge
OL,17,Fbenefits for circulation, the immune
OL,18,Fsystem and mental well-being.
