OL,3,C'An amazing way to start the day':
OL,4,CSwimmers make a splash in Alderney
OL,6,FThe latter was clearly true as the
OL,7,Fgroup met me with beaming smiles as
OL,8,Fthe sun rose over Arch Beach on the
OL,9,Fisland's north coast.
OL,11,FOne regular, Sarah Vooght, explained:
OL,12,F"It's the most amazing way to start
OL,13,Fthe day. It's not just the swim, we
OL,14,Fget out and we laugh together, we
OL,15,Fgiggle and have fun."
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Moira Sleeman couldn't wait
OL,18,Fto tell me about the soup.
