OL,3,C'An amazing way to start the day':
OL,4,CSwimmers make a splash in Alderney
OL,6,FShe told me: "It's fantastic. You'd be
OL,7,Famazed at the people who don't do it,
OL,8,Fwhy don't they do it?"
OL,10,F"The sea just begs for us to fill up
OL,11,Fwith goodness afterwards."
OL,13,FSarah and Moira were interviewed as
OL,14,Fpart of ITV Channel's 'My Community
OL,15,FSeries' which celebrates the
OL,16,Fimportance of coming together - it can
OL,17,Fbe a group of friends, a cookery
OL,18,Fclass, a sports session and much more.
